name: RetroTech - 002 - BIO ANALYSIS DEVICE
description: Not far from any Nano Particle Analyzer, you would find a 'BIO ANALYSIS DEVICE' on a nearby wall. Operators reported a lousy 48.3% accuracy in medicinal information, but opted to keep them in service as they offered a nice 'pop of color in an otherwise monochromatic space'. Second in the RetroTech series. 1080 x 1080px.
